Legislative Document No. 225
H.P. 148 House of Representatives, January 21, 2025
An Act to Reduce Property Taxes and Finance Public School
Construction and Education Through a 3 Percent Sales Tax on
Hotel and Lodging Place Rentals
Received by the Clerk of the House on January 16, 2025. Referred to the Committee on
Taxation pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed pursuant to Joint Rule 401.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative BRENNAN of Portland.
Cosponsored by Senator RAFFERTY of York and
Representatives: ANKELES of Brunswick, CROCKETT of Portland, DODGE of Belfast,
